item.description:
I HAVE A BIG EGO AND IM STEALIN ALL YO MONEYZ!!! (Read Description)
Get Tickets to the Dublin Show/Meetup! http://bit.ly/ofDG5G So why do we need tickets again? or as put by some @ssholes in the Nation,"WTF PHIL??! YOU THINK UR HOT SHIT?!?! Explanation: WE DONT WANT A CRAZY SITUATION LIKE THE LONDON MEETUP. 1400 people showed up and it was chaos. So we needed a venue, security, blah blah. So we figured why don't we give the Nation a show too?! I'll be on stage for 90+ minutes doing a Q and A along the lines of "A Night With Kevin Smith" and then afterwards we'll have a meet n greet where I get to love yo faces one at a time in a non rioty sort of way :) Turns out its expensive when you rent out a convention center, hire security, staff, sound guys blah blah blah and I CANT DO IT MYSELF. So then comes in the WHAT?!?! 20.9 Euro a ticket?!?! Yep, Its higher than I would like but in all transparency the convention center alone is costing us a ton because it was only with 2 weeks notice and thats before we even pay people to handle the event. 20 Euro includes VAT and is 12 Euros less than what they wanted me to charge per ticket. In fact I may lose some cash on this, but I wanted to at least try to meet the people of Dublin. So main point: Tickets are up.
